}

' ========== Interactions ==========
User --> BFF : Submit benchmark job

BFF --> Kafka : Publish job submission event
Kafka --> Executor : Consume job submission event
Executor --> Kubernetes : Create Kubernetes resources

Executor --> Watcher : Notify job execution start
Watcher --> Kafka : Publish job status updates
Watcher --> Executor : Provide job status updates

Kafka --> SMExecutor : Consume job submission event
SMExecutor --> AWS SageMaker : Execute benchmark job

User --> FetcherDispatcher : Request data fetching
FetcherDispatcher --> Fetcher : Create fetcher jobs
Fetcher --> S3/HTTP : Download datasets/models

Executor --> MetricsPusher : Collect metrics
MetricsPusher --> Kafka : Push metrics to Kafka
Kafka --> MetricsExtractor : Consume metrics from Kafka

CloudwatchExporter --> AWS CloudWatch : Export metrics

User --> BAICTL : Manage infrastructure
BAICTL --> AWS : Create/Destroy infrastructure using Terraform

@enduml
